Package me.philcali.device.pool.service.api.model

Class ProvisionObject.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.philcali.device.pool.service.api.model.ProvisionObject.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    ProvisionObject
    @NotThreadSafe
public static final class ProvisionObject.Builder
extends Object
    Builds instances of type ProvisionObject. Initialize attributes and then invoke the build() method to create an immutable instance.

    Builder is not thread-safe and generally should not be stored in a field or collection, but instead used immediately to create instances.
